data.title: List of books by author Philip Josè Farmer
data.meta_description: Get your Philip Josè Farmer books today! Pango Books has a huge selection of new and used titles to choose from. See all books including: Strange Relations, Tarzan Alive, Venus on the Half-Shell, Tales of the Wold Newton Universe, Stations of the Nightmare, Flesh, A Barnstormer in Oz, The Purple Book, The Other Log of Phileas Fogg, The Gates of Creation, Doc Savage, The Dark Design, Riverworld and Other Stories, The Dark Heart of Time, Dayworld Rebel, Lord of the Trees, The Book of Philip José Farmer, Lord Tyger (Grandmaster Series), Quest to Riverworld, Philip José Farmer's the Dungeon, The World of Tiers: Volume One, Jesus on Mars, Flight to Opar, The Image of the Beast, Gods of Riverworld, Dark Is the Sun, The Dark Heart of Time, The World of Tiers: Volume Two, Greatheart Silver, The Unreasoning Mask, Traitor to the Living, Ironcastle, Two Hawks from Earth, The Maker of Universes, The Wind Whales of Ishmael, Riverworld, Red Orc's Rage
